---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import logoKora from "../assets/icons/imagotipo.svg";
---

<footer class="bg-tertiary text-on-tertiary w-full rounded-t-[48px]">
  <div
    class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop py-20 flex flex-col gap-20"
  >
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <p
          class="font-label-lg uppercase tracking-widest border-b border-white/10 pb-4"
        >
          Enlaces Rápidos
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 font-body-md text-on-tertiary/60 font-thin">
          <li>
            <a class="hover:text-on-tertiary transition-colors" href="#inicio"
              >Inicio</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              class="hover:text-on-tertiary transition-colors"
              href="#propiedades-destacadas">Propiedades</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              class="hover:text-on-tertiary transition-colors"
              href="#servicios">Nuestros Servicios</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a class="hover:text-on-tertiary transition-colors" href="#nosotros"
              >Filosofía KORA</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a class="hover:text-on-tertiary transition-colors" href="#blog"
              >Blog de Diseño</a
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <p
          class="font-label-lg uppercase tracking-widest border-b border-white/10 pb-4"
        >
          Recursos
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 font-body-md text-on-tertiary/60 font-thin">
          <li>
            <a class="hover:text-on-tertiary transition-colors" href="#"
              >Centro de Ayuda</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a class="hover:text-on-tertiary transition-colors" href="#"
              >Guías de Compra</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a class="hover:text-on-tertiary transition-colors" href="#"
              >Documentación Legal</a
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <p
          class="font-label-lg uppercase tracking-widest border-b border-white/10 pb-4"
        >
          Contacto
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 font-body-md text-on-tertiary/60 font-thin">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm mt-1"
              >location_on</span
            >
            <span
              >Av. Javier Prado Este 1520, Edificio Capital, San Isidro, Lima -
              Perú</span
            >
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">call</span>
            <span>+51 1 748-0000 / +51 987 654 321</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">mail</span>
            <span>contacto@kora.pe / informes@kora.pe</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <p
          class="font-label-lg uppercase tracking-widest border-b border-white/10 pb-4"
        >
          Newsletter
        </p>
        <p class="text-white/60 text-sm font-body-md">
          Suscríbete para recibir noticias exclusivas del mercado inmobiliario
          peruano y nuevos lanzamientos.
        </p>
        <div
          class="flex bg-white/5 rounded-full p-1 border border-white/10 mt-4"
        >
          <input
            class="bg-transparent border-none focus:ring-0 flex-1 px-6 text-on-tertiary text-sm"
            placeholder="Tu email"
            type="email"
          />
          <button
            aria-label="Suscribirse"
            class="w-12 h-12 bg-white text-black rounded-full flex items-center justify-center hover:scale-105 transition-transform active:scale-95"
          >
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_forward</span>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex justify-center py-6">
      <Image src={logoKora} alt="KORA Logo" class="" />
    </div>
    <div
      class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center border-t border-white/5 pt-10 font-body-md text-on-tertiary/40"
    >
      <p>
        &copy; 2026 KORA Inmobiliaria. Exclusividad a través de la simplicidad.
        Todos los derechos reservados.
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-8 mt-4 md:mt-0 font-thin">
        <a class="hover:text-on-tertiary transition-colors" href="#"
          >Privacidad</a
        >
        <a class="hover:text-on-tertiary transition-colors" href="#">Términos</a
        >
        <a class="hover:text-on-tertiary transition-colors" href="#">Cookies</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
